snippet.title: What Programmers ACTUALLY Look Like (50,000 Special!)
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- Programmers often get stereotyped in a negative way, and I wanted to fix that. Here's what actual programmers from all over the world look like!

Programmers are people, each unique and special :)

I'd like to thank each one of you who sent in a submission and to those who wanted to be shown but were under 18.

Thank you so much for being one of my first 50,000 subscribers! It means so much to me :)

You are such great programmers!

#ILookLikeAnEngineer

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
